{"tid":1568241,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「長文」係時候嚟個中場檢討","createTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T19:27:55.000Z","uid":139484,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"2beb4b536d31de48abb088aa04de1d573821618c","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"當對家都喺度進化，有冇覺得我哋反而退步左？<br />\n七月入立法會完全冇人屌，依家熱門郁啲就話場運動就嚟散、勇武去救人就話送頭、和理非唱國歌就話懦弱。<br />\n先唔講呢啲完全散佈負能量，齋屌冇貢獻嘅post上到熱門本身已經好詭異(不推文模式啊屌)<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係我哋嘅行動力比起六七月真係退步左<br />\n唔係因為我哋收貨 或者驚左白色恐佈<br />\n係我哋個目標真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔再清晰明確</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當黑警政府藍絲個目標好清晰係做鳩我哋 打壓我哋<br />\n究竟我哋嘅目標係乜？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長遠嚟講真普選係最重要，唔係嘅話其他訴求都只會係有中國特色嘅閹割版。<br />\n不過當警藍黑三位一體，香港人短期內要爭取嘅其實係<strong>「免於恐懼的自由」</strong>。</span></span><br />\n當親政府陣營公然侵犯人權，公然侮辱毆打市民、更有合理懷疑做出強姦殺人呢啲天理不容嘅事，呢個已經係嚴重嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人道危機</span></span>，遠比爭取民主緊急好多。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">或者應該咁講：正正因為警察拒絕保護我哋，我哋需要自己組織民衛隊；正正因為政權想置香港人於死地，香港人只能借外國力量制裁港共，甚至要考慮成立臨時立法會同臨時政府。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇錯呢三個半月以嚟嘅抗爭，的確比左我哋唔少「文宣核彈」：六月醫管局同警察合作、721警察不作為同中聯辦葉虎、811爆眼女手足、監控燈柱直駁上海、新屋嶺、831太子恐襲...<br />\n隨隨便便都數到一堆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢堆「核彈」其實都指向同一個問題：依家香港有一班人，可以無視法律橫行無忌，對政府有意見嘅香港人連安全都得唔到保障。<br />\n因為相信有呢班人嘅存在，香港人未來會失去尊嚴咁生活。<br />\n所以我哋企出嚟，對抗呢種不公，討回我哋嘅尊嚴。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n應承我，唔再屌身邊手足，唔再唱淡呢場運動，一齊去攞返香港人應有嘅尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKKycZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKKycZ.png&h=dd98d27e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ofuq16j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfuq16j.png&h=896c6db8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2pRXEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2pRXEF.png&h=20ae60c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3o7vZF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3o7vZF.png&h=7d98bf35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67cd2de4f64d7cb2edbf94ea0e253b9bee818b5b","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"1/20"},{"pid":"9d3ff7e92fa0d1070d8e04fbf550d1d07393f9b0","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"2/20"},{"pid":"8b434879e76fa58ca033902d1d797559950014a6","tid":1568241,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:57:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n不指責"},{"pid":"c5ce33acd690e14a0ad0291a9a61d2cd1110aa66","tid":1568241,"uid":113587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"716829b75693b54b5f0904ed0152caddea5b9e77","tid":1568241,"uid":120174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:58:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e73df503dc497359107950d33dc7ddc373e220d","tid":1568241,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:58:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1c38012b3a7d72d0627a3b51775d83eff0232f6","tid":1568241,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"每個人都係個體，上黎開post比意見講下好處壞處<br />\n其餘既留比手足思考去唔去做 去點做就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19da796b6a17d46801a47a59c58d0d84fbacc840","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"3/20"},{"pid":"589903056720a88e26be80cada1645f64533810e","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"4/20"},{"pid":"bcfeabaf5634702268a2c64ca2f335513bf