bf0af81882921e7045","tid":1568241,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"915"},{"pid":"9222c26afb6a0107281585c4c6f0c133eb111a8c","tid":1568241,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2beb4b536d31de48abb088aa04de1d573821618c","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"當對家都喺度進化，有冇覺得我哋反而退步左？<br />\n七月入立法會完全冇人屌，依家熱門郁啲就話場運動就嚟散、勇武去救人就話送頭、和理非唱國歌就話懦弱。<br />\n先唔講呢啲完全散佈負能量，齋屌冇貢獻嘅post上到熱門本身已經好詭異(不推文模式啊屌)<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係我哋嘅行動力比起六七月真係退步左<br />\n唔係因為我哋收貨 或者驚左白色恐佈<br />\n係我哋個目標真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔再清晰明確</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當黑警政府藍絲個目標好清晰係做鳩我哋 打壓我哋<br />\n究竟我哋嘅目標係乜？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長遠嚟講真普選係最重要，唔係嘅話其他訴求都只會係有中國特色嘅閹割版。<br />\n不過當警藍黑三位一體，香港人短期內要爭取嘅其實係<strong>「免於恐懼的自由」</strong>。</span></span><br />\n當親政府陣營公然侵犯人權，公然侮辱毆打市民、更有合理懷疑做出強姦殺人呢啲天理不容嘅事，呢個已經係嚴重嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人道危機</span></span>，遠比爭取民主緊急好多。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">或者應該咁講：正正因為警察拒絕保護我哋，我哋需要自己組織民衛隊；正正因為政權想置香港人於死地，香港人只能借外國力量制裁港共，甚至要考慮成立臨時立法會同臨時政府。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇錯呢三個半月以嚟嘅抗爭，的確比左我哋唔少「文宣核彈」：六月醫管局同警察合作、721警察不作為同中聯辦葉虎、811爆眼女手足、監控燈柱直駁上海、新屋嶺、831太子恐襲...<br />\n隨隨便便都數到一堆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢堆「核彈」其實都指向同一個問題：依家香港有一班人，可以無視法律橫行無忌，對政府有意見嘅香港人連安全都得唔到保障。<br />\n因為相信有呢班人嘅存在，香港人未來會失去尊嚴咁生活。<br />\n所以我哋企出嚟，對抗呢種不公，討回我哋嘅尊嚴。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n應承我，唔再屌身邊手足，唔再唱淡呢場運動，一齊去攞返香港人應有嘅尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKKycZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKKycZ.png&h=dd98d27e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ofuq16j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfuq16j.png&h=896c6db8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2pRXEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2pRXEF.png&h=20ae60c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3o7vZF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3o7vZF.png&h=7d98bf35&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"61a844a04204640f6592f84ebb94bc809c4106e2","tid":1568241,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"53c7b6a9d8289eea2436035f5b11c812776223fd","tid":1568241,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eb24b6a7728199e3a30aa5a3a6bef52299d981c4","tid":1568241,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efb896648202bd130fba0dc2f4d9dffb80565695","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"13/20"},{"pid":"eb3784b736d5f866d8c28783f45925fbb8d1c501","tid":1568241,"uid":287206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"正經post冇人理"},{"pid":"d7845ae43cbfd88f9ed37e062ac754dc50f2b1a0","tid":1568241,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c82d5896977633f31cda2721d8a0fa2f7c974c35","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"14/20"},{"pid":"aafeb6e9cd59605e9a2bf0370283131ebeccdfcc","tid":1568241,"uid":202256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"我哋要嘅係教學po<br />\n唔係指責po<br />\n香港人學嘢咁快<br />\n推教學po一定終身受用"},{"pid":"d2624d14200d845f6e85b30a39ad3d3f9ac5d240","tid":1568241,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d19ce5db0221c7e2da1c5c62eb34b