0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"其實目標只有一個, 就係反對中國殖民香港, 所以要做既野一直都無變<br />\n<br />\n(勇武請入) 要全面升級應該學「五四運動」，抵抗紅色資本！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568436</a>"},{"pid":"64be91edbe63266519de8f5d2bf213363fea3c85","tid":1568241,"uid":43322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:56:13.000Z","msg":"主因係太多戰線 我地人多但唔足以同時打咁多敵人姐"},{"pid":"81dd98f219648e9c74129f6167386f1f5af08a0d","tid":1568241,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db03b9b4f2bee73ad91a286c1a1b35a61956f60","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"19/20"},{"pid":"af9ca9df7d11734274c1296de40c49b6c1e21da6","tid":1568241,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"連儂牆 AIRDROP<br />\n<br />\n915 915 915 915 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60d8183b07665215394d1fc5adc8896b73ef1bb","tid":1568241,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"話要扮藍絲去搞破壞班人我屌曬你地老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我地係做唔倒好似藍絲咁大肆破壞㗎<br />\n因為我地同佢地最大嘅分別係有良知<br />\n<br />\n我地之所以可以行到今時今日係因為我地唔傷及無辜<br />\n扮對家唔係等於可以放棄我地原則㗎<br />\n人地商舖得罪你啲咩要去搞人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112251f8f8aa90d984438f2d695e48c9b007b550","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"19.69/20"},{"pid":"c8d91fb2a124c12bcdab64fb8b9fb18b5d140a65","tid":1568241,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:20:09.000Z","msg":"以前佔領運動時，己經有唔少人互相指責同路人，唔知咩心態。"},{"pid":"21b9896257b2c347f15dc213a2b1b3ec9dbd638b","tid":1568241,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df248f3819a9ded7f55abb9ed78387a6c96e7c1","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"19.612/20"},{"pid":"3245090fd1621ba9beb14967b9672c495a7f5fe0","tid":1568241,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"603bb866ef5142ba761913f8dc186898e3464241","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"19.616/20"},{"pid":"171645d0486e5cb9696e4597fe14dcef962f87ff","tid":1568241,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:40:29.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"a55e433a46090fa2ac9ac881dcf8c02a3f8d9b3d","tid":1568241,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:41:00.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記 我地要攬炒"},{"pid":"3622b850c02215b0046f1a9d784694837a1b318c","tid":1568241,"uid":321546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2beb4b536d31de48abb088aa04de1d573821618c","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:54:51.000Z","msg":"當對家都喺度進化，有冇覺得我哋反而退步左？<br />\n七月入立法會完全冇人屌，依家熱門郁啲就話場運動就嚟散、勇武去救人就話送頭、和理非唱國歌就話懦弱。<br />\n先唔講呢啲完全散佈負能量，齋屌冇貢獻嘅post上到熱門本身已經好詭異(不推文模式啊屌)<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係我哋嘅行動力比起六七月真係退步左<br />\n唔係因為我哋收貨 或者驚左白色恐佈<br />\n係我哋個目標真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔再清晰明確</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當黑警政府藍絲個目標好清晰係做鳩我哋 打壓我哋<br />\n究竟我哋嘅目標係乜？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長遠嚟講真普選係最重要，唔係嘅話其他訴求都只會係有中國特色嘅閹割版。<br />\n不過當警藍黑三位一體，香港人短期內要爭取嘅其實係<strong>「免於恐懼的自由」</strong>。</span></span><br />\n當親政府陣營公然侵犯人權，公然侮辱毆打市民、更有合理懷疑做出強姦殺人呢啲天理不容嘅事，呢個已經係嚴重嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人道危機</span></span>，遠比爭取民主緊急好多。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">或者應該咁講：正正因為警察拒絕保護我哋，我哋需要自己組織民衛隊；正正因為政權想置香港人於死地，香港人只能借外國力量制裁港共，甚至要考慮成立臨時立法會同臨時政府。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇錯呢三個半月以嚟嘅抗爭，的確比左我哋唔少「文宣核彈」：六月醫管局同警察合作、721警察不作為同中聯辦葉虎、811爆眼女手足、監控燈柱直駁上海、新屋嶺、831太子恐襲...<br />\n隨隨便便都數到一堆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢堆「核彈」其實都指向同一個問題：依家香港有一班人，可以無視法律橫行無忌，對政府有意見嘅香港人連安全都得唔到保障。<br />\n因為相信有呢班人嘅存在，香港人未來會失去尊嚴咁生活。<br />\n所以我哋企出嚟，對抗呢種不公，討回我哋嘅尊嚴。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n應承我，唔再屌身邊手足，唔再唱淡呢場運動，一齊去攞返香港人應有嘅尊嚴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKKycZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKKycZ.png&h=dd98d27e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ofuq16j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOfuq16j.png&h=896c6db8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2pRXEF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2pRXEF.png&h=20ae60c6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3o7vZF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3o7vZF.png&h=7d98bf35&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"解散警隊"},{"pid":"465665de588c52ecaec6f561e7f796d7228a1522","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"19.621/20"},{"pid":"3e008246bfea22176cef507e903d46affb79b179","tid":1568241,"uid":264797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"我地需要公投<br />\n罷免現任香港政府和香港警察<br />\n禠奪合法性,向世界顯示香港人的意願"},{"pid":"caaa0e10f87bffcc65064554c689cc5c8c13f014","tid":1568241,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:55:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c973a3dd36c7e0b54b046370a0d80d85f24f74a","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:10:05.000Z","msg":"19.71/20"},{"pid":"f925b15161c6443f794b7e3b09a6159aed89e0dd","tid":1568241,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836059d55299e43b54cb2674ff9f841defa3c456","tid":1568241,"uid":139484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:21:18.000Z","msg":"19.77/20"},{"pid":"3f539bb345b7ab0ca88cf144fbb3d7bb3e5ca387","tid":1568241,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936ba668c65a910d3afdfa3496824243df4185e9","tid":1568241,"uid":117252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"ec9c5e6537d27695af9729e86f7332383745e2ae","tid":1568241,"ui